{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"joinedAt":2026.0,"programName":"USER_GROUP_LEADER"},{"category":"DevTools Hero","joinedAt":2019.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"bhuvaneswari","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/313RMAfKSMMsye5jT8OnybwA2ES.webp","bio":"Bhuvaneswari Subramani, Chief Cloud Evangelist at Intuitive.ai, is a passionate technophile and strategic leader in multi-cloud migration, application modernization, and end-to-end development.\nShe specializes in cloud service delivery, strategic alliances, and sales enablement, with deep expertise in Infrastructure-as-Code, DevOps, CI/CD, Agentic AI and AI-DLC. She also drives global outreach, mentors leaders, and bridges the gap between industry and academia.\n\nA self-made woman in tech, she has been recognized globally:\n- AWS re:Invent 2018 Diversity Scholar (https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/publicsector/meet-the-women-building-aws-technical-communities-around-the-world/)\n- AWS Community Hero (2019–2020), AWS DevTools Hero (from 2020 onwards) and featured in AWS Developer Story (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fOURKkUdtv0)\n- Honoured as AWS Hero of the Year 2022 at APJ Summit, Bangkok\n- Dr. Werner Vogel's Now Go Build Award 2022 Awardee \n- Spotlight in AWS Global Summits Video 2025 & early contributor to #AIDLC \n- Led the Navy Blue team in Road to ReInvent 2025 Hackathon, winning the title with $100K \n- She co-leads the AWS User Group Bengaluru (https://awsugblr.in/) and AWS WomenInTech India (https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-women-in-tech-india/), speaks at TEDx, global tech conferences, and universities, and blogs at https://bhuvana.saryoo.com\n\nConnect to collaborate on cloud innovation, leadership, and inclusive tech communities.","builderProfileId":"73510081-8dff-4b0b-8ed4-ef7a8a40798f","createdOn":1.718086795264E12,"headline":"","isStaff":false,"name":"Bhuvaneswari Subramani"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"IN","stateProvince":"Karnataka"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"blog":"https://installjournal.blogspot.com/","devto":"https://dev.to/bhuvanas","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/bhuvaneswari.subramani/","github":"https://github.com/bhuvana-s","linkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/bhuvanas/","personal":"https://bhuvana.saryoo.com","twitter":"https://x.com/installjournal","youtube":"https://www.youtube.com/@bhuvaneswarisubramani3038://"}}}